data.description: This new home makes a great first impression with professional landscaping and a charming covered entry. Inside, you'll find open dining and great rooms and a well-appointed kitchen featuring a center island and roomy pantry. A convenient bedroom and bathroom round out the floor. Upstairs, discover a central laundry, two generous bedrooms with a shared bath and a lavish master suite boasting an oversized walk-in closet and attached bath with linen closet. A relaxing covered patio completes the home. Adjacent to a greenbelt and park!
